SECTION A (Atempt any 6 from 8,  Marks: 5 marks x 6 question =30)
--------------
Q1. How to Connect database and check connection is established or not?

$server_name	=	"localhost";
$user_name		=	"root";
$password		=	"";
$db_name		=	"pimsat";

$mysqli=mysqli_connect($server_name, $user_name, $password, $db_name);

if(!$mysqli){

	echo "Could not connect to database";
}else{
	
	echo "data base is connected";
}

