Q.4 How to include file in PHP?

We include file in PHP by using include_once(), include(), require_once() function  and this function take one compulsory parameter.

Example : 

<?php 

	include_once("header.php");

?>

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Q.5 How to redirect your page?

 We Can redirect in two ways:

 By Using PHP:
---------------
 header("dashboard.php");  

By Using JavaScript:
--------------------
<script>window.location="dashboard.php";</script>


